- "knowledge.nyc" → use source "nyc_data"
- "knowledge.global" → use source "ue_data"
- "knowledge.madeira" → use source "madeira_data"
- "openalex" → use source "openalex"
- "pt_data" → use source "pt_data"
- "ue_data" → use source "ue_data"
- "madeira_data" → use source "madeira_data"

## Example
